&lt;h3 id=&#34;vesper&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://vesperapp.co&#34;&gt;Vesper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Evernote refugee&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:2&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:2&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;, the built-in Notes app on iOS was sufficient for me. But it was never a joy to use. &lt;a href=&#34;http://vesperapp.co&#34;&gt;Vesper‚Äôs&lt;/a&gt; attention to detail sets it apart from any other notes app.&lt;/p&gt;
