      &lt;p&gt;If one of the files doesn&amp;rsquo;t have a newline at the end and you create the unified certificate (as instructed for &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.startssl.com/?app=42&#34;&gt;StartSSL&lt;/a&gt; certs) like so:&lt;/p&gt;
