&lt;p&gt;Thankfully, the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.hnsearch.com/api&#34;&gt;HNSearch API&lt;/a&gt; makes this kind of data easy to get at so I hacked up a &lt;a href=&#34;https://gist.github.com/4419913&#34;&gt;quick script&lt;/a&gt; to do just that.&lt;/p&gt;
