&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-answers&#34;&gt;The Answers&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;UPDATE:&lt;/strong&gt; The &lt;a href=&#34;/2012/11/ruby-rebus-answers/&#34;&gt;answers post&lt;/a&gt; is now available&lt;/p&gt;
