&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f6f8fa;background-color:#82071e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;If you meant `vim&amp;#39; precisely:
