&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  desc &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Runs rake task which migrates database tables for all tenants&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
