      &lt;p&gt;If you‚Äôre trying to configure git commands in a directory that isn‚Äôt &lt;code&gt;pwd&lt;/code&gt;, you‚Äôll have to deal with &lt;code&gt;clone&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;pull&lt;/code&gt; a little differently. Clone works like this:&lt;/p&gt;
